					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Assuming your ROM has a valid internal header and no floppy copier header:<br />$20 or $30 at $7FD5 means LoROM (32K banks), and $21 or $31 at $FFD5 means HiROM (64K banks). Add $200 for a floppy copier header.</div>

